This project host a ruleset file that you can use for your configuration of maven versions plugin [http://mojo.codehaus.org/versions-maven-plugin].

Read the plugin documentation : http://mojo.codehaus.org/versions-maven-plugin/version-rules.html

To use directly the ruleset :
<rulesUri>http://www.mycompany.com/maven-version-rules.xml</rulesUri>


Test depuis un iPhone 